display="inline"><![CDATA[U]]></fr:tex> over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbb {F}]]></fr:tex></fr:li>
<fr:li><fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[I^{*}=I]]></fr:tex> where <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[I]]></fr:tex> is the identity linear transformation</fr:li>
<fr:li>If <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[L_{1}]]></fr:tex> is invertible, then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[L_{1}^{*}]]></fr:tex> is invertible and <fr:tex
